name: THE TATTOO ARTIST by The Tattoo Shop

metadata.name: Tattoo Shop #1
metadata.description: The Tattoo Shop is a collaboration of 6 world-famous tattoo artists who are releasing a series of NFTs in their genesis collection. The 1st collection, called The Tattoo Artist, is free to fans as a way of giving back. The artists involved are some of the most respected in their field, and they have come together to create a truly unique experience for fans of tattoo art. The NFTs in this collection are unlike anything else out there, and they offer a rare glimpse into the creative process of these incredible artists. The Tattoo Shop Collections are sure to have a lasting impact on the world of tattooing.
